osu-bbcode
==========

Render osu! flavoured BBCode[1] as HTML

Building
--------

To build directly in the source tree:

 $ make

To build in a separate directory:

 $ mkdir build
 $ cd build
 $ make -f ../Makefile

or

 $ make BUILDDIR=build

Usage
-----

 $ osu-bbcode [-o outfile] [infile]

Running Tests
-------------

 $ make check       # execute the test suite
 $ make memcheck    # execute the test suite with valgrind
 $ make coverage    # generage a coverage report


[1]: https://osu.ppy.sh/wiki/en/BBCode
